PrecisAppointment of Leo Hardy, of Edmonton, Alberta, as a member of the Western Aboriginal Economic Development Board and designation of the said Leo Hardy as Chairperson thereof, for a term ending December 31, 1991; appointment of Ruth Williams, of Kamloops, British Columbia, as a member of the Western Aboriginal Economic Development Board and designation of the said Ruth Williams as Vice-Chairperson thereof, for a term ending December 31, 1992; and appointment of certain persons as members of the Western Aboriginal Economic Development Board for terms ending December 31, 1991 and December 31, 1992, respectively.
